text: haey chea karpit nasa banda anakneasar robsa yeung ( mea la ai kat) ban noam damnoengola mk aoy ai pr hi m( brab tha braponth keat nung meankaun) . puokke ban svakom nung peaky sa lam haey keat kaban chhlaeyotb nung peaky sa la m vinh der . haey minyour bonman keat kaban neamk nouv kaunko ang muoy( mk ttuol puokke)
